trans-unit.source: Sorting and ordering of character data is controlled by the collation specified for a database when it is created, as well as the locale of the database. For details, see collation=collation attribute and territory=ll_CC attribute, as well as the sections "Creating a database with locale-based collation", "Creating a case-insensitive database", and "Character-based collation in " in the .
